{"type": "article", "id": 26354, "title": "推车桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-04T07:19:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144022wo27LBy3eUKzRON1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">爱带着食物到处走的吃货们，<a href=\"http://creativeans.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Creativeans</a> 设计的推车桌（trolley table）算是一大福音。如果你看到这个词觉得陌生也不必惊慌，因为这台 Wago 可能是世界上第一台能当桌子使用的推车了。当然，没有人说手推车里不能放食物以外的东西，但随着风和日丽的天气越来越多，还有什么比它更适合一场野餐之旅呢？<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144020CSuLtRUsWXwgn5EG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021440206CtpOlH2dciugzR5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144021RVZqrCNa7lcQoTGB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021440211WQa3iqrwgHlpEZ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}